Compare NBA Odds and Betting Lines

Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)

Why should I use Unabated for NBA Odds?

Unabated allows you to line shop NBA odds. Line shopping is one of the most critical tools a bettor has in their arsenal and the Unabated Odds Screen makes it easier than ever to find edges for NBA odds across sportsbooks.

What do I get for NBA odds by signing up to Unabated?

When you sign-up for Unabated Essentials, you'll get access to line history of the NBA odds, select NBA market maker odds, the compare lines feature, the NBA teaser calculator and many other betting calculators to help with your NBA betting.

Unabated Premium gives you all of the above and also includes the all NBA market maker odds, the Unabated Line for each game, in-game odds, alternate line and derivative calculators, and much more.

Click here to learn more about Unabated membership.

How can I compare NBA odds from different sportsbooks?

When you sign-up for Unabated, you can select multiple NBA odds from the Odds Screen and we will automatically compare the value of the two lines. This can also be done through our Compare Lines Calculator tool.

What NBA odds are available for comparing through Unabated's NBA Odds Screen?

We offer NBA odds for the top sportsbooks, including FanDuel Sportsbook, DraftKings Sportsbook, BetMGM, BetOnline, Bovada, and many more. Additionally, you can shop for the best NBA player props with Unabated.

Unabated subscribers will also gain access to additional market maker sportsbooks such as Bookmaker and Circa Sports, and the Unabated Line, which is a vig-free, expertly blended, consensus line from market-making sportsbooks. This is a great way to identify what the sharp price is for a market without having to know which sportsbooks are the sharpest for each sport.

Can I use Unabated for betting on NBA live odds?

Live NBA odds across all sportsbooks are available to Unabated Premium subscribers.
